@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xiaezt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.98 + 0.65)
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.74)) - wp.cos((v0 + 0.37 - tmp + 0.40)))
    tmp = ((v0 / (v2 + 0.92 + tmp + 0.43)) - ((v2 + 0.25 - v0 + 0.28) * 0.54))
    v2 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v0 = wp.abs(v2)
    v2 = (v1 - 0.69)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.85)) / tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
